<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>When I configured Zend\View\Strategy\JsonStrategy and FeedStrategy through the ViewManager, I realized there were no factories in Service Manager for these components. I think we should figure a way for ZF2 to know how to instantiate these two built in strategies.</p>

