    <div class="comment">
        <p class="metadata">Posted by Matthew Weier O'Phinney (matthew) on 2012-05-29T18:10:13.000+0000</p> 
        <div class="body">
            <p>Actually, there are -- look in Zend\Mvc\Service. It's as simple to add them as this:</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
return array(
    'view_manager' =&gt; array(
        'strategies' =&gt; array(
            'ViewJsonStrategy',
            'ViewFeedStrategy',
        ),
    ),
);
</code></pre>

<p>To make them work, there are also factories for the associated renderers.</p>

